1. *Mozak* je organ koji kontroliše sve aktivnosti našeg tela. (The brain is an organ that controls all the activities of our body.)

2. Ona je školovana da razume *mozak*. (She is trained to understand the brain.)

3. *Mozak* kontroliše naše misli i osećanja. (The brain controls our thoughts and feelings.)

4. On ne može da razume *mozak* drugih ljudi. (He can't understand the brains of other people.)

5. *Mozak* je najveći organ u ljudskom telu. (The brain is the largest organ in the human body.)

6. Naučnici su otkrili da *mozak* nastavlja da se razvija. (Scientists have discovered that the brain continues to develop.)